<div class="tag">{{type}}</div>
<h2>Hello {{userName}},</h2>
<p>There is an update regarding your organization's KYC status on the <strong>bulkmandi</strong> platform.</p>

<div style="padding: 20px; background-color: #f8fafc; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; margin: 20px 0;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1e293b;">Status: {{status}}</p>
    {{#if remarks}}
    <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">Remarks: {{remarks}}</p>
    {{/if}}
</div>

<p>You can now log in to your dashboard to see the latest updates and proceed with your transactions.</p>

<div style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="btn">View Dashboard</a>
</div>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px;">If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
